"title": "5184: standing",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5184: standing",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The bodily posture of being in a stationary upright position.</p>\n<h2>Standing as a sign of authority</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:55\">ACT 7:55</a></strong></p>\n<h2>Standing merely to wait or rest</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:21\">EXO 33:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh3:8\">JOS 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs20:38\">1KI 20:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:47\">MAT 12:47</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt20:3\">MAT 20:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:73\">MAT 26:73</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke19:24\">LUK 19:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:9\">JHN 8:9</a></p>\n<h2>Standing ready for action</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num22:23\">NUM 22:23</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:23\">ACT 5:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:8\">DEU 10:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh5:13\">JOS 5:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:16\">1SA 17:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr21:16\">1CH 21:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:11\">LUK 1:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:9\">ACT 16:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:1\">REV 7:1</a></p>\n<h2>Standing to show respect or honour</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan2:2\">DAN 2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs10:8\">1KI 10:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:19\">1KI 22:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:3\">2CH 6:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh8:4\">NEH 8:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer36:21\">JER 36:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan10:11\">DAN 10:11</a></p>\n<h2>Standing in the presence of God</h2>\n<h3>In heaven</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke1:19\">LUK 1:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech6:5\">ZEC 6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev7:9\">REV 7:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev8:2\">REV 8:2</a></p>\n<h3>On earth</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen19:27\">GEN 19:27</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:5\">EXO 3:5</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:5\">NEH 9:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod33:10\">EXO 33:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:10\">DEU 4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:10\">DEU 29:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:26\">1SA 1:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr23:30\">1CH 23:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:9\">2CH 20:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:3\">PSA 24:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer28:5\">JER 28:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:5\">MAT 6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:25\">MRK 11:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:11\">LUK 18:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:4\">ROM 14:4</a></p>\n<h2>Standing for trial or judgment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod18:13\">EXO 18:13</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:10\">ROM 14:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num5:16\">NUM 5:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num35:12\">NUM 35:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut19:17\">DEU 19:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:3\">1SA 12:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:7\">1SA 12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech3:1\">ZEC 3:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt27:11\">MAT 27:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:32\">LUK 11:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:6\">ACT 23:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts25:10\">ACT 25:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev20:12\">REV 20:12</a></p>\n<h2>Standing firm as a believer</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov10:25\">PRO 10:25</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:58\">1CO 15:58</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:28\">LUK 21:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:2\">ROM 5:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:20\">ROM 11:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor15:1\">1CO 15:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:13\">1CO 16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:21\">2CO 1:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:24\">2CO 1:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:1\">GAL 5:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil4:1\">PHP 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:12\">COL 4:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:15\">2TH 2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas5:8\">JAS 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:12\">1PE 5:12</a></p>\n<h3>Against evil and temptation</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:13\">1CO 10:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:11-Eph6:14\">EPH 6:11–6:14</a></p>\n<h3>Against enemies and opposition</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps94:16\">PSA 94:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:13\">EXO 14:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr20:17\">2CH 20:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa7:9\">ISA 7:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer1:17\">JER 1:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:11-Eph6:14\">EPH 6:11–6:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:27\">PHP 1:27</a></p>\n<h2>Other metaphorical uses of standing</h2>\n<h3>God's purpose will stand</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa46:10\">ISA 46:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa14:24\">ISA 14:24</a></p>\n<h3>Standing in the gap</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek22:30\">EZK 22:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:23\">PSA 106:23</a></p>",
